35:13.912 --> 35:18.550 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, more than two months in
office, Mr. Trump
has shaken up the world stage,
from dust-ups

35:18.583 --> 35:22.721 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
with longtime allies to
continued questions
about Russia.

35:22.754 --> 35:27.859 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We examine the administration's
foreign policy
now with two veteran lawmakers
who helped

35:27.892 --> 35:34.065 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
