able to have
impulse control or delayed
gratification are

47:16.801 --> 47:18.703 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
able to save more money.

47:18.736 --> 47:22.673 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
PAUL SOLMAN: But how to
encourage kids to
delay gratification?

47:22.707 --> 47:26.644 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Start, says Kobliner, by not
giving in to
every demand.

47:26.677 --> 47:31.315 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BETH KOBLINER: You know, we're
going to go
into the store right now and
we're only getting

47:31.348 --> 47:35.820 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
